reviewText: My husband is a big fan. So I bought him this
Story is very compelling...because it's TRUE. They did a good job on an obviously limited budget. If ur looking vh1 Behind the Music, you will immediately become upset. I don't HATE it though

Was super excited when I got this Dvd. Opened it up put it in and sure enough its the same exact disc as screaming black messiahs. Everything from the title screen to the lame "extras". Only difference is the artwork that comes with it. Talk about a rip off.
